OL,4,CRosemary Nelson protection 'in
OL,5,Chindsight'
OL,7,FThe Northern Ireland Office (NIO)
OL,8,Fshould have done more to offer
OL,9,Fprotection to murdered solicitor
OL,10,FRosemary Nelson, a top official
OL,11,Faccepted "in hindsight", according to
OL,12,Fnewly released documents.
OL,14,FMrs Nelson was killed by a loyalist
OL,15,Fcar bomb outside her home in Lurgan,
OL,16,FCo Armagh in March 1999.
