OL,7,FThe 40-year-old mother of three's
OL,8,Flegal practice dealt with mainly
OL,9,Froutine cases, but she rose to
OL,10,Fprominence after taking on a number of
OL,11,Fhigh-profile clients.
OL,13,FThey included suspected republican
OL,14,Fterrorists as well as the family of a
OL,15,FCatholic man murdered by a loyalist
OL,16,Fmob, plus a nationalist residents'
OL,17,Fgroup opposing Orange Order parades in
OL,18,Fthe infamous Drumcree stand-off.
