OL,8,Fallege security force intimidation and
OL,9,Freported receiving death threats from
OL,10,Floyalists.
OL,12,FHer claims that RUC officers were
OL,13,Fthreatening her while interviewing her
OL,14,Fclients echoed the experience of
OL,15,FBelfast solicitor Pat Finucane, who
OL,16,Fwas shot by loyalists in 1989.
