OL,7,FHowever, he suspected she would not
OL,8,Fhave welcomed an RUC security offer,
OL,9,Fthough he said he would have liked
OL,10,Flighting installed that would have
OL,11,Filluminated "the entire front of the
OL,12,Fhouse and would also have detected any
OL,13,Finterference with her vehicle".
OL,15,FRUC Chief Constable Ronnie Flanagan
OL,16,Fbelieved the bombing had to have been
OL,17,Fcarried out "in some form" by members
