OL,7,FOne of Mrs Nelson's clients, Gary
OL,8,FMarshall, claimed that he had been
OL,9,Ftold during interrogation by the RUC
OL,10,Fat Castlereagh "that Rosemary works
OL,11,Ffor the IRA and takes her orders from
OL,12,Fthem".
OL,14,FJust days before she was killed, Mrs
OL,15,FNelson contacted the Department of
OL,16,FForeign Affairs fearful about her
OL,17,Fsafety, with an official noting: "She
OL,18,Fis very worried and asked if it would
OL,19,Fbe possible to meet with the Minister
OL,20,Fto discuss her case."
