OL,7,F"As a result of this, the Special
OL,8,FRapporteur's office is proposing to
OL,9,Fdelete the names of the solicitors
OL,10,Ffrom the report. Ms Nelson considers
OL,11,Fthis to be a meaningless exercise as
OL,12,Feverybody will know the solicitors the
OL,13,Frefers to," the Irish Government
OL,14,Fdocument states.
OL,16,FAn inquiry into Mrs Nelson's death
OL,17,Ffound no direct security force role in
OL,18,Fher murder, but said it could not rule
OL,19,Fout that "rogue" elements may have
OL,20,Fassisted the killers.
